        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "On a critical hit, the weapon adds a weapon damage die of the listed size. Roll this after doubling the weapon\u2019s damage. This increases to two dice if the weapon has a <i>greater striking rune</i> and three dice if the weapon has a <i>major striking rune</i>. For instance, a rapier with a <i>greater striking rune</i> deals 2d8 extra piercing damage on a critical hit. An ability that changes the size of the weapon\u2019s normal damage dice doesn\u2019t change the size of its deadly die.",
